[microphone hums]

00:01:45.563 --> 00:01:48.441 position:50% align:center
[YU] I have a little favor to
ask of you, if that's all right.

00:01:48.525 --> 00:01:51.444 position:50% align:center
Please beat this girl
in a landslide victory.

