and tell me why.

00:11:19.721 --> 00:11:23.391 position:50% align:center
I... I, uh...

00:11:23.475 --> 00:11:25.935 position:50% align:center
The thing I wanna say is...

00:11:29.731 --> 00:11:31.566 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]

00:11:31.649 --> 00:11:32.942 position:50% align:center
Go ahead.

00:11:34.194 --> 00:11:35.945 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:36.029 --> 00:11:37.447 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Jeez.

00:11:37.530 --> 00:11:38.740 position:50% align:center
She would have self-destructed

00:11:38.823 --> 00:11:41.201 position:50% align:center
if he'd just left
well enough alone.

