He'll lend a helping hand
to anyone who needs it.

00:20:23.348 --> 00:20:26.101 position:50% align:center
I was never someone
special to him.

00:20:28.645 --> 00:20:30.230 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA gasps]

00:20:30.313 --> 00:20:32.065 position:50% align:center
Since you've got so much to say,

