00:20:55.714 --> 00:20:58.550 position:50% align:center
I threw away your hard work
by acting on impulse.

00:20:58.633 --> 00:21:01.177 position:50% align:center
I feel bad about it, but...

00:21:01.261 --> 00:21:04.055 position:50% align:center
I only did it because
I had Fujiwara, Ishigami,

00:21:04.139 --> 00:21:06.224 position:50% align:center
