That's why... I want you
to be my vice president.

00:21:23.867 --> 00:21:26.911 position:50% align:center
I need you, Shinomiya.

00:21:26.995 --> 00:21:28.329 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA gasps]

00:21:35.879 --> 00:21:37.881 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI gasps]

00:21:37.964 --> 00:21:39.174 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Yes!

00:21:46.514 --> 00:21:48.099 position:50% align:center
Well, would you look at that?

00:21:48.183 --> 00:21:51.019 position:50% align:center
You got your special
treatment after all.

00:22:06.242 --> 00:22:07.702 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Okay!

00:22:08.912 --> 00:22:11.122 position:50% align:center
The election is over
and done with.

